{
  "stem": "9156.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Today, I understand that they must have been very hurt, because I insisted that, I cannot go to the university right away-- here, I was crying for that-- but that I have to become a laborer in a factory.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I have to know how it feels to make your living that way.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Again, not unusual for some of those idealistic young people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But I do understand that it was hard for them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I also felt I had to leave Berlin, that I had to go somewhere else, just start differently.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And we're doing this as fast as I can.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I went to Hamburg.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, I forgot that when this politicizing came, I had to find a group because we had split.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I find-- found another group.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was the ISK, I-S-K.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That stands for Internationale Sozialistische Kampfbund.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "K-A-M-P-F-B-U-N-D.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they are-- they were, for a long time, part of the Social Democratic Party.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They separated from it because they were more active than they felt the Social Democrats were.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They felt they were becoming too soft.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they had a leader, Leonard Nelson, N-E-L-S-O-N, who was a university professor at Goettingen, G-O-E-T-T-I-N-G-E-N.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he had started a special school, because his idea was that democracy doesn't work.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You have to educate people to be totally selfless.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Oh, there's a lot there that I don't agree with it anymore.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But at the time, it was something.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I met these people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Among them, I'll give a name, Maria Hoddann, H-O-D-D-A-N-N.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And she was a very intelligent woman, very thoughtful.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
